The People&rsquo;s Paper has once again been voted the Coolest Daily Newspaper in Mzansi.This according to youths between the ages of eight and 23 who voted for their favourite brands in the Sunday Times Generation Next Awards.The Daily Sun beat out nine other publications including, The Times, The Star, and the Sowetan.Our sister publication, Sunday Sun came out third place in the Coolest Weekly Newspapers category.The awards are an annual survey which measures the &ldquo;coolness&rdquo; of brands and celebrities in Mzansi.The survey is run through the HDI Youth Marketeers and each year, thousands of kids choose the coolest brands of them all.WATCH: BABES SHAKES IT FOR THE KIDS AT #GENNEXT2017!